commit.message:
(LINK_LIBGCC_SPECIAL): Defined.

(DBX_OUTPUT_STANDARD_TYPES): Check that DECL_NAME(decl) exists
before trying to get its IDENTIFIER_POINTER.

From-SVN: r1555

 /* Most of the Alliant-specific definitions here are to get stab info that
